                            辉羽宝卷——圣教会苏生明王偈
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/canon-hub">设定中心</a> &raquo; <a href="/doctors-of-the-church-hub">教会博士 中心页</a> &raquo; 辉羽宝卷——圣教会苏生明王偈
                        </div>
                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+22</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<div style="padding: 1px 15px;position:relative;">
<div style="left:40px;position:relative;font-size:200%;font-family:'微软雅黑';">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;◇&nbsp;题&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;◎&nbsp;题&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><span style="font-size:50%;"><strong>何日</strong>：虎牢攻陷后，甲子已十轮<br />
<strong>焉在</strong>：神州教所中，早课流传经忏声<br />
<strong>孰作</strong>：羽天一<br />
<strong>采风者</strong>： 䟅<br />
<strong>札</strong>：<br />
本欲愚民以造神，自欺欺人反以为真也。<br /></span></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<hr />
<div style="background: url(&quot;http://kaktuskontainer.wdfiles.com/local--files/format-hell/scp_trans.png&quot;) center no-repeat;width:100%">
<div class="ej-outbox">
<div class="ej-innerbox">
<div class="poem-7">
<p><br />
幽幽玄月嚎莽苍，潜影祟魔夜未央<br />
<br />
忽奏洪钟歌妙法，黑云震裂彻华光<br />
<br />
华光穿户陟灵台，洞照哲石显上皇<br />
<br />
应世苏生弥赛亚，归心高赞大明王<br />
<br />
身携诸圣化先师，语缀诸经为首章<br />
<br />
异教失诚窥祸乱，众氓皈礼复荣昌<br />
<br />
<a href="/oria-001">尔时业火卷天下</a>，<a href="/competitive-eschatology-hub">跃马四骑引饿狼</a><br />
<br />
瑟瑟寒风糅暗泣，孰蛰昏秽起彷徨<br />
<br />
曾祈昊宇垂甘露，曾探<a href="/about-the-serpent">大渊</a>乞禁方<br />
<br />
天地悠悠何寂寂，却飘蛛线远油汤<br />
<br />
谁惊妖魅啸雷音？谁处黯极绽玉芒<br />
<br />
唯有君恩须永念，虔心复赞大明王<br />
<br />
<a href="/scp-2317">百贤受领轰朱鬼</a>，<a href="/scp-682">挥索缚龙封入箱</a><br />
<br />
<a href="/quid-est-non-scitum">宝卷一开阐戒律</a>，<a href="/o5-command-dossier">十三弟子牧八荒</a><br />
<br />
共闻教导解虚惑，俱顺欣欣竞作羊<br />
<br />
<a href="/indwelling-of-bright">更待罪人皆获救</a>，<a href="/scp-963">魂眠精链自安详</a><br />
<br />
愿为迷途求赦宽，赐民一苇渡炎江<br />
<br />
<a href="/by-one-iota">愿为愚徒请谛言</a>，赐民正法满庭芳<br />
<br />
愿随君道辟福田，愿与君仆亲义长<br />
<br />
愿聚萤德争日月，至心久赞大明王<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br /></p>
</div>
</div>
